eligibilityModule.eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Stroke - ischemic type;
* Dysphagia following stroke;
* 40 to 70 years old;
* Exclusive enteral Feeding;
* Glasgow \> 11.

Exclusion Criteria:

* Pregnants;
* Febrile Condition;
* Neoplasia;
* Pacemaker;
* Cochlear Implant;
* Anxious Patient;
* Degenerative Neurological Diseases.
